thProver

Class CNFFormula

  • java.lang.Object
    • thProver.CNFFormula

  • public class CNFFormula
extends java.lang.Object
    A CNF formula - a set of clauses. Contains clauses, literals, atoms and terms of the given formula It's the class used by parser to construct the graph representing the formula
